Incident Management	âœ… (reactive)	âœ… (proactive and reactive)
Automation	âœ… (delivery focus)	âœ… (toil reduction focus)
Collaboration & Culture	âœ… (Agile/Lean focus)	âœ… (reliability engineering culture)
System Reliability	ğŸš«	âœ…
SLOs, SLIs, Error Budgets	ğŸš«	âœ…

ğŸ” Summary
ğŸ’¼ DevOps Engineer = "Build fast, test faster, release safely."
Focus: Automation, delivery speed, environment setup.

ğŸ’¼ SRE Engineer = "Keep the system reliable, performant, and scalable."
Focus: Uptime, observability, incident response, system health.
